's
job
in
0000
.

Mr.
<_UNK>
,
00
years
old
,
declined
to
be
interviewed
for
this
article
,
but
he
has
consistently
argued
that
over
the
long
haul
--
across
both
the
peaks
and
the
troughs
of
the
plastics
market
--
Quantum
will
prosper
through
its
new
direction
.

Quantum
's
lot
is
mostly
tied
to
polyethylene
resin
,
used
to
make
garbage
bags
,
milk
