action
.
''

Of
course
,
the
health
of
the
economy
will
be
threatened
if
the
market
continues
to
dive
this
week
.

Sharply
falling
stock
prices
do
reduce
consumer
wealth
,
damage
business
confidence
and
discourage
the
foreign
investors
upon
whom
the
U.S.
now
relies
for
financial
