.

The
financial-services
industry
was
battered
by
the
0000
crash
.

What
's
more
,
although
the
stock
market
is
far
less
overvalued
today
than
two
years
ago
,
the
U.S.
economy
is
weaker
.

Growth
is
slower
.

Profits
are
softer
.

Debt
burdens
are
heavier
.

But
if
the
stock
market
does
n't
continue
to
plummet
,
the
beneficial
effects
of
lower
interest
rates
and
a
lower
