.

But
the
experience
of
the
0000
crash
suggests
the
Fed
is
likely
to
bring
down
short-term
interest
rates
in
its
effort
to
calm
markets
.

Anticipating
the
Fed
's
move
,
money
traders
lowered
a
key
interest
rate
known
as
the
Federal
Funds
rate
to
0.000
%
late
Friday
,
down
